      "content": "idk, it just sounds super weird. like you're saying there's no actual signal or anything moving between them, so how does the second one even \"know\" what the first one did? it sounds almost like some kind of magic or a glitch. is there any way to actually test if it's real or if it's just some hidden variable we haven't found yet?",
